      <title>穆勒称欧洲央行必须耐心进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/ecb-must-be-patient-with-further-interest-rate-cuts-muller-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员麦迪斯·穆勒表示，欧洲央行可能在年底前再次降低借贷成本，但不应着急这么做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/ecb-must-be-patient-with-further-interest-rate-cuts-muller-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 07:05:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金多斯称欧洲央行未遵循预定的利率路径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/guindos-says-ecb-not-following-pre-determined-interest-rate-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行副行长路易斯·德金多斯在接受 CNBC 采访时表示，由于不确定性仍然很高，欧洲央行不会按照预先设定的路径降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/guindos-says-ecb-not-following-pre-determined-interest-rate-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 06:50:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
